OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FTemperatures across the UK are
OL,7,Fexpected to ease slightly on Thursday
OL,8,Fafter a heatwave that saw record highs
OL,9,Fset for the month of May.
OL,11,FThe Met Office is forecasting highs of
OL,12,F31C in London and 28C in the Midlands
OL,13,Fand North West, which, while still
OL,14,Fhot, is noticeably lower than the
OL,15,F35.1C recorded at Kew Gardens in west
OL,16,FLondon on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
