PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780002672
OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FThe forecaster also said on Wednesday
OL,7,Fthat another "tropical night", where
OL,8,Ftemperatures remained above 20C, was
OL,9,Funlikely. ITV Weather presenter Nick
OL,10,FMiller explained that this phenomenon
OL,11,Fwas unprecedented for the UK so early
OL,12,Fin the year.
OL,14,FSeveral records were broken earlier
OL,15,Fthis week, with the 35.1C recording in
OL,16,FKew Gardens not only setting a new
OL,17,Frecord for May but also beating Kew's
OL,18,Fhighest June temperature.
OL,26,@oD@NOUoD@]O]
