OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,F"A warm start to Thursday with
OL,7,Fshowers, possibly thundery, pushing
OL,8,Fnorthwards and clearing northern
OL,9,FEngland," it said in a post on X.
OL,10,F"Temperatures soon rising with
OL,11,Fsunshine turning hazier in the west."
OL,13,FThe Met Office's outlook for Friday to
OL,14,FSunday says: "Largely dry with sunny
OL,15,Fspells and very warm once again on
OL,16,FFriday.
OL,18,F"A band of rain then gradually spreads
OL,19,Feastwards over the weekend,
OL,20,Fintroducing some fresher and possibly
OL,21,Fshowery conditions."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]rD@AOUsD@eO]vD@NOUzD@AOU}D@
