OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FThe hot weather has also attracted
OL,7,Fmany to open water swimming, resulting
OL,8,Fin a number of deaths in South
OL,9,FYorkshire, West Yorkshire, Cornwall,
OL,10,FHampshire, Warwickshire, Cheshire,
OL,11,FPembrokeshire, Lincolnshire and
OL,12,FLancashire in recent days.
OL,14,FDeclan Sawyer, 15, died after getting
OL,15,Finto trouble at Swanholme Lakes,
OL,16,FLincoln, on Sunday. That same day, a
OL,17,F72-year-old woman died after being
OL,18,Fpulled from the water at West Angle
OL,19,FBay beach in Pembrokeshire, Wales.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
