OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FA 13-year-old boy, understood to be
OL,7,Fnamed Reco Puttock, died after getting
OL,8,Finto difficulty at Leadbeater Dam,
OL,9,Fnear Halifax, West Yorkshire, on
OL,10,FMonday, while the body of a teenage
OL,11,Fgirl was recovered from the water at
OL,12,FKingsbury Water Park, Warwickshire.
OL,14,FThe same day, a man in his 60s died of
OL,15,Fcardiac arrest after entering the sea
OL,16,Fat Tregirls Beach, Padstow, to help
OL,17,Ftwo family members who were in
OL,18,Fdifficulty, Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
