OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FThe body of a teenager was recovered
OL,7,Ffrom the water at Rother Valley
OL,8,FCountry Park, Rotherham, in the early
OL,9,Fhours of Tuesday morning, South
OL,10,FYorkshire Police said.
OL,12,FAnother body has been found in the
OL,13,Fsearch for a teenage boy who went
OL,14,Fmissing after he was last seen
OL,15,Fswimming at Hawley Lake on the
OL,16,FHampshire/Surrey border on Tuesday
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
