OL,3,CTemperatures expected to ease after
OL,4,Crecord-breaking heatwave
OL,6,FA 12-year-old boy who died after
OL,7,Fgetting into trouble in the River
OL,8,FRibble at Ribchester, Lancashire, on
OL,9,FTuesday was named as Junior Slater
OL,10,Ffrom Clayton-le-Woods.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Cheshire Police said the
OL,13,Fbody of a 17-year-old boy was found
OL,14,Fafter he went missing in Pickmere Lake
OL,15,Fat Marston, Northwich.
